{"tid":757550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近3年逾百警員被捕　休班警佔大半","createTime":"2018-07-27T02:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T00:45:39.000Z","uid":28366,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef39062483656b53ded815c93b85eea85dc29f2","tid":757550,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/105806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F105806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=75613bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員操守近年備受關注。警務署回覆立法會財委會議員的數據顯示，2015至2017年每年分別有35、43及29名警員被捕，當中各年分別有22、33及23名屬休班警。全體被捕警員中，這三年分別有19、34及18人是被警方拘捕。此外，每年分別有16、9及11名警員被其他執法部門拘捕，例如廉政公署及海關。<br />\n<br />\n被警方拘捕的警員中，2015至2017年分別各有15、21及15人，涉嫌干犯警隊定義為罪行性質屬較嚴重的刑事案件，當中19人涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢／打鬥、刑事毀壞及破壞公眾體統、遊蕩等罪行，有7人涉嫌傷人及嚴重毆打、6人涉嫌雜項盜竊。涉嫌非禮、詐騙或店舖盜竊的，各有5人；涉嫌強姦、襲警、刑事恐嚇或車輛內盜竊，則各有1人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180418/s00001/1524063240071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180418%2Fs00001%2F1524063240071&d=rPk%2BqPz8NcK6ymllK2Cm5W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a558a874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180418%2Fs00001%2F1524063240071&h=c8cdeefc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180418/s00001/1524063240071</a>"},{"pid":"73e44591d89e4e48dbbaf024f3a981fc79af455a","tid":757550,"uid":41423,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"平均十日一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780fba176d8c77153e96bdad3043ec0602efb970","tid":757550,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73e44591d89e4e48dbbaf024f3a981fc79af455a","tid":757550,"uid":